# Title
Makefile de conveniencia

# File
## Makefile
```make
.PHONY: up down logs sh seed clean build
up: ; docker compose up --build -d
down: ; docker compose down
logs: ; docker compose logs -f --tail=100
sh: ; docker compose exec app sh || true
seed: ; @echo "Seed se ejecuta automáticamente si la DB está vacía."
clean:
	docker compose down -v
	rm -f provider/users.db
build: ; docker compose build
```
